metadata.name: SWOOPAHS #1
metadata.description: Swoopahs are the Guardians of Creativity. Only 555 exist in the world and their home must be protected. They live in Greenwood Forest and speak using a special language called Swoopish. In exchange for helping Swoopahs stay safe, these sky fairies use their magic to inspire the modern renaissance. A place where ideas, art, and community reign supreme. They are small, but mighty.
